/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d49c0c40beb6f1bd16a4a15816695fcc799fad6","tid":498744,"uid":160692,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:16:36.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友喺擦紙膠公司做過，佢同我講，因為想刺激銷量，增加需求，公司入面有個部門專門派人去學校、自修室同補習社偷擦膠，所以之前先會有影子學生。<br />\n<br />\n其實所謂嘅影子學生，就係偷擦膠嗰啲人。<br />\n<br />\n時薪有五十五蚊，okay好揾。"},{"pid":"b9ada57692f62b6f849e9eddad4ec522dbb03013","tid":498744,"uid":161352,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"研究發現用得完一個擦膠既極高機會係潛在罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用得完既都係心理變態"},{"pid":"2e4e4d07c0f39556cc9d4759560bbba3d86b1f34","tid":498744,"uid":10396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"次次未用到一半就唔見"},{"pid":"6b519647c29bade96791691590c9d65168bb57c9","tid":498744,"uid":24926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢樣真 由細至大 用到咁上下都會唔知去左邊"},{"pid":"051b59602e604e221ad1cc5dae1b1cbf9655d26e","tid":498744,"uid":54387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"試過keep住用，又小心唔會整唔見<br />\n<br />\n但到咁上下舊擦膠會解體，解體後細粒到擦唔到"},{"pid":"bc5fed00dc717670778a3a2e727f6e305f66dc4f","tid":498744,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"擦膠有腳是常識吧"},{"pid":"4d3c7183d02fcb3e74a34f63576e5b6a244b72a0","tid":498744,"uid":33429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/170029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F170029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3a2e9241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知由15定16歲開始用到21歲都未用得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />